OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA dry and
OL,6,Fclear night to come with perhaps a few
OL,7,Fmist and fog patches forming. Breezy
OL,8,Faround coasts. A chilly night with
OL,9,Fperhaps a frost in the countryside.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTuesday:FA sunny start to the day,
OL,12,Falthough high cloud will gradually
OL,13,Fbuild in from the west making the
OL,14,Fsunshine hazy by lunchtime. Feeling
OL,15,Fwarm, especially in the sunshine.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
