OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,6,FStaying largely fine and warm on
OL,7,FWednesday, but rain will move in from
OL,8,Fthe west later. Cooler and showery on
OL,9,FThursday. Likely turning wet and windy
OL,10,Fon Friday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
